{"word":"καπνίζω","slug":"καπνίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καπνίζω</b></el> <el>(καπνίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:καπνός'><el>καπνός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to make smoke</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>to make a fire</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to smoke, blacken with smoke</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to be black with smoke</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}